com.github.lecogiteur.csvbang.annotation
Annotation Type CsvHeader

@Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Inherited
@Documented
public @interface CsvHeader

Annotation in order to define header of CSV file

Version:
0.1.0
Author:
Tony EMMA

Optional Element Summary
 String customHeader
          You can define your custom static header.
 boolean header
          Display the header on the first line.
 

header

public abstract boolean header
Display the header on the first line. By default false. The header is generated with the name of field and keeps the defined order of field. If no name is defined for a field, we take the property name or method name

Returns:
True or false
Since:
0.1.0
Default:
false

customHeader

public abstract String customHeader
You can define your custom static header. By default no custom header is defined. If header() is set to true, the custom header is written before the generated header.

Returns:
the custom header
Since:
0.1.0
Default:
"null"
